(17, 8, 'tt_port_smalltext', 'Identity and website'),
(20, 8, 'tt_port_description', '<p>Sven Faulconer is a Los Angeles based filmscore producer from Belgian descent. I was contacted by Sven because his site was outdated and he was in dire need of upgrading his online presence. His site needed to stand out in the competitive market in LA, so we started working on an identity and portfolio and came up with a paralax design with integrated music player and sound database. We made it easy for music producers and movie studios to browse and listen to his latest work.</p>\n'),
(21, 8, 'tt_port_clients', '<p>Sven Faulconer</p>\n'),
(22, 8, 'tt_port_skills', '<p>Graphic Design</p>\r\n'),
(27, 13, '_edit_last', '1'),
(28, 13, '_edit_lock', '1420214067:1'),
(32, 13, 'tt_port_smalltext', 'design of the YARIS-Elegance special edition logotype'),
(33, 13, 'tt_port_description', '<p>I was asked by Happiness-Brussels to come up with a logotype for the new line of the Toyota YARIS-Elegance. The brief was to create a logotype that reflects style, simplicity and value for a young and energetic audience. The final typeface would be used on the car as an embossed metallic logo  and for POS materials. For the same campaign I developed a short advertising animation for LED screens at the Belgian football stadiums.</p>\n'),
(34, 13, 'tt_port_clients', '<p>Happiness Brussels</p>\n'),
(35, 13, 'tt_port_skills', '<p>Graphic Design</p>\r\n'),
(36, 17, '_edit_last', '1'),
(37, 17, '_edit_lock', '1420215254:1'),
(47, 17, 'tt_port_smalltext', 'Logo design and branding'),
(48, 17, 'tt_port_description', '<p>Rindu is a brand of handmade jewelry from Belgium, made in Indonesia, with Indonesian materials, started by Katty Demeyer in 2010. Katty was looking for a redesign of her logo and was missing meaning in her visual identity. ''Rindu'' is a word in the Indonesian language and translates into ''to miss''. I visually translated this concept into parts of the word ''rindu'' that are ''missing''. Merging content and form into one logotype that has elegance and completes the ''rindu'' concept.</p>\n'),
(49, 17, 'tt_port_clients', '<p>Rindu</p>\n'),
(50, 17, 'tt_port_skills', '<p>Advertising</p>\r\n'),
(51, 22, '_edit_last', '1'),
(52, 22, '_edit_lock', '1421512317:1'),
(61, 22, 'tt_port_smalltext', 'Online presentation of the collaboration Levi''s x Sangra'),
(62, 22, 'tt_port_description', '<p>During my years at Levi''s Europe many times we worked on collaborations, however Danny Sangra''s stood out because his quirky style. For his collection I worked on an animation based interactive presentation that was published on the levis.eu website.<br />\nwarning: Flash</p>\n'),
(63, 22, 'tt_port_clients', '<p>Levi''s Europe</p>\n'),
(64, 22, 'tt_port_skills', '<p>Advertising<br />\r\nGraphic Design</p>\r\n'),
(72, 27, '_edit_last', '1'),
(73, 27, '_edit_lock', '1421271376:1'),
(79, 27, 'tt_port_smalltext', 'Poster design'),
(80, 27, 'tt_port_description', '<p>Brussels based Fuel-design briefed me on the concept and design for a poster for CIDSE, an european union workshop held in Brussels. The idea of the poster was to visualize the mindshift this workshop creates.</p>\n'),
(81, 27, 'tt_port_clients', '<p>Fuel-design Brussels</p>\n'),
(82, 27, 'tt_port_skills', '<p><span class="portfolio-meta-value">Branding<br />\r\n</span>Graphic Design</p>\r\n'),
(83, 32, '_edit_last', '1'),
(84, 32, '_edit_lock', '1421270478:1'),
(94, 32, 'tt_port_smalltext', 'Logo and Corporate Identity'),
(95, 32, 'tt_port_description', '<p>Georgia is a social club and allows people to discuss business in a social environment. We wanted to be simple and  serious ... with a twist.</p>\n'),
(96, 32, 'tt_port_clients', '<p>Georgia</p>\n'),
(97, 32, 'tt_port_skills', '<p>Branding</p>\r\n'),
(105, 37, '_edit_last', '1'),
(108, 37, 'tt_port_smalltext', 'IFoam concept and poster design'),
(109, 37, 'tt_port_description', '<p>The brief for this project was to create an identity for the 10 year existence of the European Organic Advocacy. For this case I used illustrations to form the ''10'' and create an identity for the concept.</p>\n'),
(110, 37, 'tt_port_clients', '<p>European Union<br />\nFuel Design</p>\n'),
(111, 37, 'tt_port_skills', '<p><span class="portfolio-meta-value">Branding<br />\r\n</span><span class="portfolio-meta-value">Graphic Design</span></p>\r\n'),
