(703, 195, 'text_left_image_right_1_text_column_left_right', '<p class="line-1">You need me for your...\r\nlogo design/corporate ID/print design/visual brand identity/\r\nweb &amp;amp; app architecture/website design and development/application design and development/video post and production/</p>\r\n<p class="line-2">If you’re looking for a design studio that will push you and your company, <a href="http://#" target="_blank">drop me a line</a>,send me a letter or smoke-signal me.</p>'),
(704, 195, '_text_left_image_right_1_text_column_left_right', 'field_5477e11b9725a'),
