(946, 294, 'text_and_image_0_text_column_left_right', '<h3>Kiokarma is a one man design studio. A good one.</h3>\r\nMore than anything else, I’m a creative. I get to the core of what you – or your business – are about, and deliver you the media that puts the best of it on display.\r\n\r\nI primarily design logos, identities and websites but i’m always up for a challenge and never limit my creativity through a medium or technology.'),
