(1222, 336, 'text_and_image_0_text_column_left_right', '<h3>Kiokarma is a one man design studio. A good one.</h3>\r\nMore than anything else, I’m a creative. I get to the core of what you – or your business – are about, and deliver you the media that puts the best of it on display.\r\n\r\nI primarily design logos, identities and websites but i’m always up for a challenge and never limit my creativity through a medium or technology.'),
(1223, 336, '_text_and_image_0_text_column_left_right', 'field_5477e11b9725a'),
(1224, 336, 'text_and_image_0_image_column_left_right', '291'),
