(1226, 336, 'text_and_image_1_text_column_left_right', 'I believe that good graphic design is a visual interaction between content and form, without content, form is useless. You don’t want to change your logo when it goes out of trend, and neither do I so I design for the long haul, contemporary timeless.\r\n\r\nWith +10 years of experience in design I’ve had the priviledge to work with and for the finest people and brands in the business, which didn’t go unnoticed. My work has been featured in design books like <a class="gestaltenLink" href="http://localhost/PHP/BLISS/Yves/www/BE/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/gestalten_verlag_supersonic_kiokarma_1.jpg">Supersonic of Gestalten Verlag</a> and <a class="indexbookLink" href="http://localhost/PHP/BLISS/Yves/www/BE/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/gestalten_verlag_supersonic_kiokarma_1.jpg">Indexbook of Around Europe.</a>'),
(1227, 336, '_text_and_image_1_text_column_left_right', 'field_5477e11b9725a'),
(1228, 336, 'text_and_image_1_image_column_left_right', '292'),
(1229, 336, '_text_and_image_1_image_column_left_right', 'field_5477e13c9725b'),
(1230, 336, 'text_and_image_2_text_column_left_right', '<p class="line-1">You need me for your…\r\nlogo design/corporate ID/print design/visual brand identity/\r\nweb &amp;amp; app architecture/website design and development/application design and development/video post and production/</p>\r\n<p class="line-2">If you’re looking for a design studio that will push you and your company, <a href="http:/#" target="_blank">drop me a line</a>,send me a letter or smoke-signal me.</p>'),
