(1667, 452, 'tt_port_projects', '<p>Peter Van Riet, long time friend and talented product designer started working on a new concept of snowboard binding. After a few prototypes the first Beyondsnow™ binding was launched in 2008. In close collaboration with Peter, Kiokarma took care of the graphic part of the beyond story. For multiple seasons Kiokarma worked on the full visual identity and branding as also the product graphics, POS materials, website, apparel, packaging and other print media.</p>\n<p>Brand Identity<br />\nArt direction<br />\nProduct graphics<br />\nPackaging design<br />\nPOS materials<br />\nPrint material<br />\nWebsite</p>\n'),
