(289, 1, '2014-12-04 02:45:59', '2014-12-04 02:45:59', '<div class="service">\r\n<div class="pad">\r\n<h3>Kiokarma is a one man design studio. A good one.</h3>\r\n<div class="text">\r\n<div class="pad">More than anything else, I’m a creative. I get to the core of what you - or your business - are about, and deliver you the media that puts the best of it on display.</div>\r\n<div class="pad">I primarily design logos, identities and websites but i’m always up for a challenge and never limit my creativity through a medium or technology.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- end .service -->\r\n<div class="service hasImg"><img class="size-full wp-image-183 alignleft" src="http://localhost/PHP/BLISS/Yves/www/BE/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/ab-1.jpg" alt="ab-1" width="682" height="378" /></div>\r\n<!-- end .service -->\r\n<div class="service hasImg"><img class="size-full wp-image-185 alignleft" src="http://localhost/PHP/BLISS/Yves/www/BE/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/ab-2.jpg" alt="ab-2" width="682" height="378" /></div>\r\n<!-- end .service -->\r\n<div class="service">\r\n<div class="pad">\r\n<div class="text">\r\n<div class="pad">I believe that good graphic design is a visual interaction between content and form, without content, form is useless. You don’t want to change your logo when it goes out of trend, and neither do I so I design for the long haul, contemporary timeless</div>\r\n<div class="pad">With +10 years of experience in design I’ve had the priviledge to work with and for the finest people and brands in the business, which didn’t go unnoticed. My work has been featured in design books like\r\n<a href="#" target="_blank">Supersonic of Gestalten Verlag</a> and\r\n<a href="#" target="_blank">Indexbook of Around Europe.</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- end .service -->\r\n<div class="service service-3">\r\n<div class="pad">\r\n<div class="text">\r\n<p class="line-1">You need me for your...\r\nlogo design/corporate ID/print design/visual brand i